Subject: [PATCH 5.12 002/173] ASoC: max98088: fix ni clock divider calculation
Date:   Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:25:34 +0200
Message-Id: <20210614102658.231240876@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.32.0
